{
  "text": "It was described that myxomatous emboli frequently leads to formation of cerebral aneurysms and may lead to severe neurologic complications such as intracerebral hemorrhage [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "20937001"
